text: Kate McKinnon Berthold (born January 6, 1984), commonly known as Kate McKinnon, is an American actress, voice actress, and comedian. She is best known for her sketch comedy work as a cast member on Saturday Night Live (2012-2022) and The Big Gay Sketch Show. == Career == McKinnon is known for her impersonations of Secretary of State Hillary Clinton, Ellen DeGeneres, Justin Bieber, Attorney General Jeff Sessions, Chancellor Angela Merkel, Trump advisor Kellyanne Conway, Mayor Rudy Giuliani, U.S. Senator Lindsey Graham, Secretary of Education Betsy DeVos and Associate Justice Ruth Bader Ginsburg. McKinnon is SNL first openly lesbian cast member. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:1984 births Category:Living people Category:Actors from New York City Category:LGBT people from New York City Category:LGBT comedians Category:LGBT actors Category:Lesbians Category:American movie actors Category:American television actors Category:American voice actors Category:Comedians from New York City
